snippet.textDisplay: I just want to say thank you for all of the AMAZING videos you create! I have been subscribed for about 2 months now and I LOVE going through and watching all of your videos! I am currently in College working towards a Nursing Degree and finishing up a course to be a Certified EMT and all of your videos are so informational and put it in a simple and fun video. Your humor in each video makes them fun and I love learning more about what I have learned or am learning using your channel. You clarify a myriad of complicated subjects for me! This channel deserves a lot more recognition than it gets! Thank you and please keep up the great work! Please support this channel!
